        @{i}/L@{ui}ist [class]

@{b}DESCRIPTION@{ub}
        @{b}/List@{ub} will list all feelings available in this BBS. Optionally
        you can specify a feeling class to list only feelings belonging
        to that spesific class.

        Available classes are:

        affectionate
        aggressive
        audible
        friendly
        funny
        inferior
        malignant
        negative
        positive
        red (communist)
        superior
        tactile (physical, touching)
        vulgar
        white (monarchist)

